cat << EOF
PlayOnLinux is a piece of software which allows you to easily install and use 
numerous games and apps designed to run with Microsoft Windows. Few games are
compatible with GNU/Linux at the moment and it certainly is a factor preventing
the migration to this system. PlayOnLinux brings a cost-free, accessible and
efficient solution to this problem.
EOF
